        "heading": "Usage Instructions",
        "text": "<h2>Usage Instructions</h2><p>[wistia_video]</p><p>To get started with your first treatment, you'll need the following:</p><ul><li>1 sterile needle head (provided)</li><li>Micro-Infusion serum vial (provided)</li></ul><p>Ensure your hands are clean before and during the treatment and do not rush yourself.</p>"
      }
