      "name": "t:sections.n_guide-content-image-block.name",
      "settings": {
        "use_own_file": true,
        "active": false,
        "must_read": false,
        "heading": "Serum Ingredients & Information",
        "text": "<h2>Serum Ingredients & Information</h2><p>Each Qure Micro-Infusion treatment is powered by a single-use ampoule of concentrated serum, designed to target specific skin concerns with clinically backed ingredients.</p><p>These serums are lightweight, fast-absorbing, and free from fragrance, parabens, and harsh actives.</p>"
      }
    },
    "n_guide_content_dTJNe3": {
      "type": "n_guide-content",
      "name": "t:sections.n_guide-content.name",
      "settings": {
        "use_own_file": true,
        "active": false,
        "must_read": false,
        "heading": "Product Claims",
        "text": "<h2>Product Claims</h2><p>Key claims:</p><ul><li>Single-use disposable needle-heads with 24 karat gold-plated needles minimize the risk of infection and irritation.</li><li>Delivers science-backed serums directly to skin to help increase absorption & results.</li><li>Little to no downtime & quick recovery of the skin.</li><li>Great alternative to in-clinic microneedling.</li><li>User study shows that the Micro-Infusion System improves overall skin appearance, with the most noticeable results seen in the appearance of pores and wrinkles.</li></ul><p>Results from a 12-week user study:</p><ul><li>70% of participants say their fine lines looked smoother.</li><li>93% noticed results the next day after their first micro-infusion treatment.</li><li>70% of participants say their skin looked brighter and more even toned.</li></ul>",
        "slides_per_view": ""
      }
    },
    "n_guide_content_VqPkmU": {
      "type": "n_guide-content",
      "name": "t:sections.n_guide-content.name",
      "settings": {
        "use_own_file": true,
        "active": false,
        "must_read": true,
        "heading": "Content Requirements",
        "text": "<h2>Content Requirements</h2><p>Messaging must include:</p><ul><li>How it works</li><li>How to use</li><li>Information about the serums and the specific skin concerns they treat.</li><li>Affordable and convenient at-home 5-minute treatment that costs up to 15X less than professional in-clinic treatments</li></ul><p>Content ideas:</p><ul><li>Before and After</li><li>How to use and product details</li><li>Comparing Micro-Infusion to alternatives</li><li>What experts say/expert review</li></ul>",
        "slides_per_view": ""
      }
    },
    "n_guide_content_8LbzGQ": {
      "type": "n_guide-content",
      "blocks": {
        "quote_AKKTbf": {
          "type": "quote",
          "settings": {
            "style": "blue",
            "text": "<p><strong>Tag and mention</strong> @qureskincare #quremicroinfusion #microneedling #microinfusion #athomefacial #wellageing #qure #qureskincare</p><p>Include your affiliate or other links provided by Qure in Instagram Stories and content captions. If the link can’t be placed in bio, include it in linktr.ee or similar.</p>"
          }
        },
        "image_slider_zdk63x": {
          "type": "image_slider",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/mi_creative-guide1.webp"
          }
        },
        "image_slider_3qqqLc": {
          "type": "image_slider",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/mi_creative-guide2.webp"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "quote_AKKTbf",
        "image_slider_zdk63x",
        "image_slider_3qqqLc"
      ],
      "name": "t:sections.n_guide-content.name",
      "settings": {
        "use_own_file": true,
        "active": false,
        "must_read": false,
        "heading": "Creative Direction",
        "text": "<h2>Creative Direction</h2><p>Recording Guidelines</p><ul><li>Use bright, natural lighting. No filters.</li><li>Keep backgrounds clean and uncluttered.</li><li>Ensure the Qure Micro-Infusion and serums are the main focus of the content.</li><li>When demonstrating the application, ensure your skin is makeup-free (or with no visible makeup) to keep the results authentic and easy to see.</li><li>Include clear close-ups during use to show technique and effectiveness.</li><li>Be sure to include before-and-after visuals to highlight visible improvements—ideally captured in similar lighting and framing for credibility and consistency.</li><li>In cover photos for video content always show yourself using the Qure Micro-Infusion (unless agreed otherwise).</li></ul>",
        "slides_per_view": "2"
      }
    },
    "n_guide_content_EjiAY3": {
      "type": "n_guide-content",
      "blocks": {
        "text_slider_N4pjRB": {
          "type": "text_slider",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>Why Didn't I Try This Sooner?</strong></p><p>Cost-effective alternative to in-clinic treatments. Highlight ease, convenience, and noticeable results.</p><p>[note_grey]<strong>Hook:</strong>“I spent $$$ on facials—then I found this at-home tool that changed everything.”[/note_gray]</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_slider_PWphPp": {
          "type": "text_slider",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>Preventative Botox Alternative</strong></p><p>In the long run, consistently hydrating and supporting your skin with tools like micro-infusion is a smarter foundation for well-aging than relying solely on preventative Botox.</p><p>[note_grey]<strong>Hook:</strong>“I do have an opinion on preventative botox, but it might be a controversial one...”[/note_grey]</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_slider_CwbFGJ": {
          "type": "text_slider",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>Does It Hurt?</strong></p><p>Although it sounds intimidating, micro-infusion uses ultra-fine, gold-plated needles that gently create tiny, micro-channels— enhancing serum absorption and it feels like velcro.</p><p>[note_grey]<strong>Hook:</strong>“Stabbing your face with needles! Sounds terrifying, but here is a reason why you might want to do this.”[/note_grey]</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_slider_QNEici": {
          "type": "text_slider",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>What Skincare Feels Like When It Actually Absorbs</strong></p><p>Highlight enhanced absorption, micro-channel delivery, and ingredient efficacy.</p><p>[note_grey]<strong>Hook:</strong>“Here's why your anti-aging creams are disappointing you...”"
          }
        },
        "text_slider_ztbtYC": {
          "type": "text_slider",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>Stubborn Dark Spots?</strong></p><p>Topical creams often sit on the surface, but micro-infusion delivers brightening ingredients beneath the skin barrier—helping to fade stubborn dark spots more effectively by targeting them at the source.</p><p>[note_grey]<strong>Hook:</strong>“Have dark marks like this that won't seem to fade with creams? Here's what you need to know”[/note]</p>"
          }
        }
      },
